sub_title: Lecturer of Russian as Foreign Language
summary: Experienced lecturer of Russian as a foreign language with 14 years of practice; trained over 5000 students. I teach Russian without any intermediate language using the methodology developed by the Institute of Russian Language, St. Petersburg, Russia. I work with students ranging from elementary level up to C2 (fluent Russian in professional activity) and had successfully prepared a lot of students for certification exams.
